{"tid":965573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★雌支鬼 乘小巴強行打尖，港人𡚒力抵抗，支鬼戰敗！","createTime":"2019-01-02T07:04:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-02T07:21:21.000Z","uid":19454,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6d3d6bc77c620880caaddebfd9d2d7101947bc3c","tid":965573,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T07:04:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190102/photo/bkn-20190102135052190-0102_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190102141310\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190102%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190102135052190-0102_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190102141310&h=0d4b8b86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n排隊是維持秩序的良好方法，惟近日有大媽打尖衝上小巴，更拍卡坐低，結果被司機乘客齊心驅趕，更設計迫她落車。<br />\n<br />\n有乘客在其Facebook專頁「哈弟Hadee─我由乜乜徒步到乜乜」講述事件，指星期二（1日）凌晨近3時正在荃灣等於小巴，當時站頭有約50人正排隊候車。未料當小巴到站時，有一名操普通話的婦人突然祟出並衝上小巴。司機即時大聲喝止︰「排隊呀」！<br />\n<br />\n她聲稱自己有排隊，但司機激動地反駁︰「望住你打尖啦，後面排緊咁多人你見唔到㗎？呢度係香港，唔係大陸，落番去排隊啦」！<br />\n<br />\n但大媽卻厚着臉皮，取出八達通拍卡並坐下，司機只好熄匙堅持不開車，批評大媽是「慣犯」，每日如是。全車乘客亦團結一致，齊聲斥︰「落車啦你」。<br />\n<br />\n未料大媽仍然無動於衷，並說︰「我不怕你們」、「你打我唄」、「我頭痛呀」。有肥仔乘客遂搶走大媽手上的電話，衝落車放在地上。<br />\n<br />\n「阿姐要喺小巴同手機之間做選擇，佢兩樣都想要，所以企喺車門樓梯，係咁大叫︰『把手機還我』」。最終在無人幫忙下，她被迫妥協，「佢離開架車嗰刻，司機極速撻匙開車，阿姐轉身粗口都講唔切，我哋已經掰掰佢條尾」。<br />\n<br />\n網民紛紛讚揚司機及車上乘客非常團結︰「正氣司機和肥仔好波」、「終於有人出聲」、「呢啲就係香港精神囉」！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190102/bkn-20190102135052190-0102_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190102%2Fbkn-20190102135052190-0102_00822_001.html&d=cFyyBEaL9oyRSxvD5eL3%2B7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=cff618f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190102/bkn-20190102135052190-0102_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"44a684d72b28e9014802f1ed27207b7cc4c0d65f","tid":965573,"uid":19454,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T07:05:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OXwS2Kv.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOXwS2Kv.gif&h=93b8161d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a143541b64f98f05b6a14625173ceade55ceeb96","tid":965573,"uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T07:06:08.000Z","msg":"司機好波"},{"pid":"abac34601b82594b682ac6835d87b84885d956b4","tid":965573,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a143541b64f98f05b6a14625173ceade55ceeb96","tid":965573,"uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T07:06:08.000Z","msg":"司機好波"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T07:06:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19e6bde7fb75ef7c4a11498f750a9ace3ff7212b","tid":965573,"uid":6548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T07:07:26.000Z","msg":"有冇片睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45852188ff151a62a94d18a27f23e6904d22842b","tid":965573,"uid":90820,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T07:07:31.000Z","msg":"肥仔好嘢司機好嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n根本見到就應該一齊幫口<br />\n唔係走去屌鬧人嗰個阻住開車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"621b98bdd49fbbdde0199b0702bfdf6d7b7c78e0","tid":965573,"uid":34949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T07:07:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d68b1cf30a426da262d23358ba2ababa5d44a3d1","tid":965573,"uid":53705,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T07:10:20.000Z","msg":"每日150個新移民<br />\n將來只會更多呢D事<br />\n<br />\nD大陸人係大陸唔洗排隊, 所以佢地去到世界各地都係咁"},{"pid":"f7dc0a3c79abd150b8ed1018ac0276215e7d1efc","tid":965573,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T07:11:11.000Z","msg":"香港人秩序<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"326803c98eb8000e1a2100867ea2f64b63e4715a","tid":965573,"uid":665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T07:16:24.000Z","msg":"今次呢個咪好司機囉<br />\n平時個時見你嘈都唔理你照開車 咪撚煩到佢揸車<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dda5d19413efe7b04646a8b76f77d973c13f4197","tid":965573,"uid":57023,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T07:21:21.000Z","msg":"HK要每天接收150件呢類垃圾咁多年, 人地星加坡只吸菁英, 有乜辨法人地唔抛離HK呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}